metadata.name: Forged by Light
metadata.description:
The Ethereal Dance collection celebrates a feminine energy that is free flowing and not bound by rules.

"Forged by Light" depicts a rebirth, as the female form floats in ethereal space. She is enlightened. She is made up of stars. 

Made with Adobe. "Forged by Light" is a 3D illustration that is digitally hand painted, texturized with my photography, and brought to life with star stuff. 

All Copyrights Reserved 2023

License - The collector has the right to display this artwork in any form of gallery, online or physical as a part of their own collection. The purchase of this 1/1 NFT is a purchase of the asset, not of the copyright.
